article_id:144,category_name:Events,title_name:Epilogue added to the Resplendent Refrain raid event ,image_path:,message:<div>An epilogue has been added to the raid event Resplendent Refrain, which ended <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1544594399"></span>.</div><div><br></div><div>You can view the epilogue by tapping the banner on the top left of the Home screen, which you can access from the footer menu.</div><div><br></div><div>■Epilogue availability:</div><div><span class="local_date" data-local_date="1544594400"></span> to <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1545199199"></span></div><div><br></div><div>■Note:</div><div>The epilogue can be viewed only by players who have completed up to chapter 5 of this event&#39;s story before its end.</div><div><br></div><div>Thank you for playing Dragalia Lost!</div>,start_time:1544594400,update_time1545359266